{#
/**
 * @file
 * Theme for displaying brewery homepage
 *
 * The template included in the brewery_homepage module only displays a short
 * message. To stay organized, the actual implementation of this template
 * can be found in the brew theme.
 */
#}
{{ attach_library('brew/homepage') }}

{# The feature band is a large image and a placeholder for the site title. #}
<div class="homepage-feature">
  <div class="homepage-feature__title wow zoomInLeft"></div>
</div>

{# The story band incldues intro copy. #}
<div class="content-band content-band--story">
  <div class="content-band__content wow fadeIn">
    <h1 class="content-band__heading">
      Push Your Pallet
    </h1>
    <div class="content-band__break"></div>
    <div class="content-band__body">
      Beer is an acquired taste. My first IPA was undrinkable. And I remember my
      first brett beer to be truly nasty. But I kept trying new things and now I
      wouldnâ€™t dare turn down a hoppy or sour beer.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{# The stats band has a bubble effect that shows brew counters. #}
<div class="homepage-stats">
  <div class="homepage-stats__background"></div>
  <div class="homepage-stats__content">
    <div class="bubble wow fadeIn">
      <div class="bubble__inner">
        <div class="bubble__count" id="brewery-count"></div>
        <div class="bubble__type">Breweries</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bubble wow fadeIn">
      <div class="bubble__inner">
        <div class="bubble__count" id="brewpub-count"></div>
        <div class="bubble__type">Brewpubs</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bubble wow fadeIn">
      <div class="bubble__inner">
        <div class="bubble__count" id="taproom-count"></div>
        <div class="bubble__type">Taprooms</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="myTargetElement" id="myTargetElement"></div>

{# The final content bands appears at the bottom of the page. #}
<div class="content-band content-band--welcome">
  <div class="content-band__content wow fadeIn">
    <h1 class="content-band__heading">
      My Beer Travels
    </h1>
    <div class="content-band__break"></div>
    <div class="content-band__body">
      I rarely drink the same beer twice. Instead I explore the craft beer
      scene one flight at a time; supporting local businesses and indulging
      my inner hipster.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
